        <div class="wrapper">
            <p>Line Posters first came about when visitors suggested to the founders that they start selling their artwork of the New York subway. Do you think you can <strong>name all the NY subway lines</strong>? Start typing below to begin.</p>
            <div class="circles">
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
                <div class="circle"></div>
            </div>
            <input type="text" maxlength="1" placeholder="Type here" onkeyup="app.trivia.mta.checkInput(this)" />
        </div>
    </div>
{{/ifCond}}
{{#ifCond title '==' 'Off Road China'}}
    <div class="trivia off-road">
        <div class="wrapper">
            <p>The Off Road trekkers previously lived in China for several years before publishing and writing a cook book detailing their experience. <strong>Which of the following did <em>not</em> originate from China?</strong></p>
            <span class="message"></span>
            <div class="multiple-choice">
                
                <label class="button purple add-margin" for="off-road-choice-a">
                    <input type="radio" name="off-road" id="off-road-choice-a" value="a">
                    A. Rice
                </label>

                <label class="button purple" for="off-road-choice-b">
                    <input type="radio" name="off-road" id="off-road-choice-b" value="b">
                    B. Noodles & pasta
                </label>
                
                <label class="button purple add-margin" for="off-road-choice-c">
                    <input type="radio" name="off-road" id="off-road-choice-c" value="c">
                    C. Fortune cookies
                </label>

                <label class="button purple" for="off-road-choice-d">
                    <input type="radio" name="off-road" id="off-road-choice-d" value="d">
                    D. Alcohol Beverages
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{{/ifCond}}
{{/each}}